  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Techniques: Black, Blue, Green, Purple, Red, Perfect </p><p></p><p>You're skilled at using your Puppet Tool as a way to get what you want out of a conversation.</p><p> While engaged in a social conversation and your Puppet Tool is present nearby (or you are wearing your Juggernaut Armor), you can choose to give yourself proficiency in Persuasion , Performance, or Intimidation temporarily.</p><p> If you are already proficient, you gain a +1d6 bonus to the roll.</p><p> A creature can be affected by this upgrade twice per hour.</p><p> You must narrate the context for what you or your Puppet is doing to gain the benefits of this upgrade (Ex.</p><p> Intimidating a foreign invader, your Puppet gives a threatening stare; You are trying to impress someone, and your Puppet gives them a smile).</p><p></p>",
